  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses provisions related to injuries from dog attacks.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>establishes that an individual injured in a dog attack may bring a claim for damages within four years of the injury; <hr><ltbullet>raises the maximum award from $50,000 to $75,000 in arbitration and at trial for a bodily injury claim resulting from a dog attack, not including certain costs; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
